map. While we are not providing guidance for years beyond 2024, we expect c=
apex will continue to increase next year as we invest aggressively to suppo=
rt our ambitious AI research and product development efforts.

The market reception to Microsoft and Google, though, could not be more dif=
ferent than the reaction to Meta; from Bloomberg ( https://www.bloomberg.co=
m/news/articles/2024-04-26/microsoft-google-gain-after-ai-fuels-cloud-compu=
