The tech titans have been locked in a fierce battle for dominance in the fi=
eld of artificial intelligence, with Microsoft joining forces with startup =
OpenAI to challenge Google=E2=80=99s two-decade stranglehold on internet se=
arch. But Thursday=E2=80=99s results showed there=E2=80=99s ample room for =
both companies to grow.

Microsoft is the best positioned to benefit from AI in the short-term: firs=
