mplement AI into their businesses; Azure grew 31% with 7 points of that gro=
wth coming from AI services. 1 ( #fn1-12865 ) Second, they have an enterpri=
se software business that can expand its average revenue per user by sellin=
g AI services; Microsoft didn=E2=80=99t report how many CoPilot seat licens=
es they sold, but they did say it contributed to Office 365=E2=80=99s 15% g=
rowth in commercial revenue. These clear opportunities for monetization, al=
ong with the potential upside of AI generally, should and do make investors=
 happy about the additional capex investment.

